<h1>Ardent University</h1>
<d1>
<b>Ardent University</b> is a distance and blended learning university, with its head office in Coventry, England. Formerly a family-owned business known as Resource Development International it was awarded university status by the British government in 2015. Since August 2016 it has been been owned by Global University Systems.

